  <brief_title>Evaluate SAGE-547 in Female Patients With Severe Postpartum Depression</brief_title>
  <official_title>An Open-Label Proof-of-Concept Study Evaluating the Safety, Tolerability, Pharmacokinetics, and Efficacy of SAGE-547 Injection in the Treatment of Adult Female Patients With Severe Postpartum Depression</official_title>
  <sponsors>
