  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is an open-label proof-of-concept study designed to evaluate the safety, tolerability,
      PK, and efficacy of SAGE-547 Injection in adult female patients diagnosed with severe
      postpartum depression (PPD).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
